Entries.default: "That right there is why you always check for traps."
"That looks like a warning."
"Hey, they're pretty good at that."
"When did they learn to do that?!"
"I don't see the point. Heh... Ishi gets it."
"Almost enough to make one feel self-conscious."
"Just once, can't these things appear someplace nice?"
"Anybody got a chisel and some wheelbarrows?"
"Even in this state, it's easy to see why luminous adra is so prized."
"That rock be a pound or two of gold, cap... if you can get it into our hold."
"You seeing what I'm seeing? It's got to be the peak."
"Stay sharp."
"Unfortunate. Let us not repeat history."
"Poor swabby. Still, better a spike in the side than a spear up the rear."
"What got that poor soul... let's not let it get us."
"Reminds me of the ranga nui's shooting gallery."
"Come no closer, fiends!"
"Madiccho! They're coming up the walls!"
"Avast! Next time we be bringing the boarding netting!"
"Watch your back, Watcher! They're coming up the walls!"
